<P>
TODAY'S QUOTE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
"If I just keep thinking, 'I'm in Tahiti. I'm in Tahiti,' then this heat 
doesn't bother me." -- Sarah Daniels, a secretary in the UCLA cardiac unit, 
where the air conditioning was out until mid-afternoon. 
</P>
