<HEADLINE>
<P>
GENTLEMEN, START YOUR SAILBOATS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Having loved Jim Murray's work since my dad introduced me to it more than 30 
years ago, I am temporarily saddened by his suggestion that New York Supreme 
Court Justice Carmen Ciparick's decision on the America's Cup was anything but 
brilliant and daring. 
</P>
<P>
One need only read the chronology of events to understand the unsportsmanlike 
conduct of the defenders. 
</P>
<P>
When gentlemen accept the terms of a duel, it is not general practice to have 
one armed with a derringer and the other with a submachine gun. 
</P>
<P>
But who said we were talking about gentlemen? 
</P>
<P>
RON HOLDER 
</P>
<P>
Laguna Niguel 
</P>
</TEXT>
