FOREIGN RELATIONS -- SYRIA; SYRIA -- ARMED FORCES; CHRISTIANS; BEIRUT 
(LEBANON); MIDDLE EAST PEACE; FRANCE -- FOREIGN AID -- LEBANON 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
