(SHIP); COAST GUARD (U.S.); BUSH, GEORGE; EXXON CORP; SKINNER, SAMUEL K; YOST, 
PAUL; UNITED STATES -- ARMED FORCES; OCEAN POLLUTION; WATER POLLUTION -- 
ALASKA; POLLUTION CONTROL 
