(SHIP); COAST GUARD (U.S.); BUSH, GEORGE; EXXON CORP; EXXON SHIPPING CO; 
SKINNER, SAMUEL K; YOST, PAUL; UNITED STATES -- ARMED FORCES; OCEAN POLLUTION; 
WATER POLLUTION -- ALASKA; POLLUTION CONTROL; GULF OF ALASKA; ANIMAL DEATHS; 
NATIONAL OCEANIC AND ATMOSPHERIC ADMINISTRATION 
</P>
