ACQUISITIONS; AIRLINE WORKERS -- WAGES AND SALARIES; AIRLINES -- LABOR 
RELATIONS; PILOTS; MACHINISTS; FLIGHT ATTENDANTS; SUITS; TEXAS AIR CORP; 
BANKRUPTCY; TRANS WORLD AIRLINES 
</P>
