Jeffrey, 12, and daughter Chris, 19. AURELIO JOSE BARRERA / Los Angeles Times; 
Photo, Myra Brown, retired social worker from Newport Beach, who will be 
marching for women's rights for the first time Los Angeles Times 
</P>
