EL TORO CATCHER TOPPO WILL ATTEND UC IRVINE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Scott Toppo, El Toro High School catcher, has made a verbal commitment to 
attend UC Irvine in the fall and plans to sign a national letter of intent on 
Wednesday, the first day a high school player is allowed to sign. 
</P>
<P>
Toppo, batting .381 in his second season as a starter, plans to become a second 
baseman in college. 
</P>
